# API And Types Synchronization

When API payload or endpoint behavior changes:

- Update both `src/lib/api.ts` and `src/types/api.ts` in the same task.
- Keep hook usage aligned with DTO changes (`src/hooks/*`).
- Prefer additive, backward-safe contract evolution when possible.

# Contract Safety

- Do not rename/remove DTO fields used by existing UI without updating all consumers.
- Keep endpoint paths/params aligned with documented contracts in `AGENTS.md`.
- If backend contract is uncertain, flag it and ask instead of guessing.
